### StudExE4 User Service API Tests
### Requires the "REST Client" extension in VS Code
### Run the server first: `cd services/user-service` -> `go run cmd/server/main.go`

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081

### 1. Get All Users (For testing/admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

### 2. Register New User via WhatsApp Bot (Only Phone Number)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phone": "628555555555"
}

### 3. Personalize User (Update Name & Gender)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/628555555555/personalize
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Siti",
    "display_name": "Siti A.",
    "gender": "Female"
}

### 4. Delete User (For testing)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/6285331886336
